The Alex Jones Show

Friday March 6th, 2009.

Hour-1: News and open lines

Hour-3: News and open lines

Jason Bermas holds down the Infowars command center while Alex is away. Jason welcomes Tennessee Rep. Susan Lynn, who has filed a resolution to affirm Tennessee's sovereignty under the Tenth Amendment. Additional guests include Prison Planet editor and journalist Paul Joseph Watson and Bob Chapman of the International Forecaster. Jason runs down the important news of the day and takes your calls.
